\n我做過果間 最長14日<br />\n睇啲油幾時換<br />\n早餐炒蛋"},{"pid":"5c85c9ca00e44b9ac6db568131316cb12f6efae9","tid":6824,"uid":30714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾耐換一次油？<br />\n<br />\n麥樂雞係咪最好唔好叫？<br />\n<br />\n咩食物最安全衛生？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個星期換一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個間就星期五/六換<br />\n其實炸既野啲油係唔係用左好耐 有樣睇<br />\n安全衛生？飲生業冇依樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食物最安全衛生真係冇乜<br />\n買23蚊餐 啲麥樂雞 辣腿用用左好耐既油<br />\n買至尊少人食既餐 啲牛肉又煎左好耐 放係到唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下你撞唔撞正佢換油個日會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6730232aceb9875fff150c078752adb43d7e74c1","tid":6824,"uid":24747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>儲左幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係咁洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去左兩次旅行 買左部iPhone <br />\n依家得返2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點儲到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f10476fd9d643f971876ce11e35c5eac24d18703","tid":6824,"uid":30714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T15:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>儲左幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係咁洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去左兩次旅行 買左部iPhone <br />\n依家得返2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點儲到咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前真係返得好瘋狂 其實時薪冇你地諗得咁低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b338529a6dc